me.zingle.api.sdk.dao

Class QueryPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.zingle.api.sdk.dao.QueryPart

  • public class QueryPart
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience class for request modifiers. Represents key-value pair of one modifier, which is translated to request modifier. For example key=page, value=2 will add page=2 modifier to HTTP request.
